// The Wronged Moves
.sheet-OPBHead.sheet-MinorHead.sheet-space-above(data-i18n='the-wronged') The Wronged
.sheet-Wronged
	i
		span(data-i18n='1-fixed-move') You get this
	| :
.sheet-Wronged.sheet-OPB
	input.sheet-triggerbox.sheet-ExpToggle(type='checkbox', name='attr_Toggle-MovesUnused', value='1', checked='')
	.sheet-move
		input.sheet-checkbox(type='checkbox', name='attr_FixedMoves-Wronged1')
		span.sheet-mainbox
		|  
		span.sheet-grayable
			span(data-i18n='wronged-fixed-move1')
				b I Know My Prey
				| : You get +1 ongoing when knowingly investigating, pursuing, or fighting the breed of monster that caused your loss.
